<P>"That the faith of the State be pledged for the punc|tual payment of the intere&s;t, and that the intere&s;t and monies receivable from the United States by <HI>Penn&s;ylva|nia</HI> or &s;o much thereof as may be nece&s;&s;ary be appro|priated to that purpo&s;e, provided always that the Le|gi&s;lature may withdraw this appropriation upon provid|ing other adequate and &s;ufficient funds.</P>
